{
  "title": "Dense Hangover-Cure Turkish Pork Back Ribs Grill",
  "description": "A flavorful, comforting Turkish-inspired dish featuring pork back ribs, pickles, and a hint of spice to help tackle a hangover. Perfect for a late-morning brunch or a quick dinner.",
